    fw_cfg: add required header files
    
    If fw_cfg.h is included alone, gcc gives error messages like these:
    
      error: unknown type name ‘uint32_t’
      error: unknown type name ‘size_t’
      error: unknown type name ‘hwaddr’
      ...
    
